    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You have to see this absolute beauty! It is in truly flawless condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for that 'brand new' feel without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you\u2019re going to love it! \u2728",
      "price": 44500.0,
