    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a collector-grade example of the ultimate driving machine, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with double-VANOS timing and individual throttle bodies. The mechanical integrity is superlative, with documented rod bearing replacement and proactive rear subframe reinforcement already completed. Power is managed via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M-differential lock, ensuring visceral feedback and precise corner-exit traction. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, riding on a flawlessly maintained suspension setup that eliminates any lateral play. With a pristine exterior finish and an interior devoid of typical bolster wear, this vehicle represents a turnkey investment for the discerning purist.",
